# Testing Rules

## Backend Testing
- Vitest is configured in `apps/backend/vitest.config.js`
- Test files: `*.test.js` co-located with source files
- MongoDB must be running for integration tests
- Mock external services where possible

## Commands
```bash
pnpm test                      # Run all tests
pnpm --filter ./apps/backend test  # Run backend tests only
pnpm --filter frontend test        # Run frontend tests only
```
